Description:
You arrive at a dry oasis and see a heron doing a strange dance, as you approach he says:

"I am desperate, I need rain no matter what to fill the oasis and have enough water reserves.

Perhaps one of you is able to make it rain? If not, will you join me in my dance to see if it rains?
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
